{
  "stem": "3855.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when I saw this fighting over this little quarter-inch piece of a cigarette, I started to understand human nature better, and addiction, and then decided that I'd never smoke.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I saw these pogroms, if you wish, in Poland, I also decided that, when it came to drinking, it wasn't going to my-- one of my weaknesses.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I admit, I'll have a glass of wine with dinner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that is about all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so those two things stuck in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I decided it's just not for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the episode with cigarettes is so vivid in my mind that I wanted to bring it out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Many other people came to me and said, we saw you help these older people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You saved their lives.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I never looked at it that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I thought it was a natural thing to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some of these older people could have been my parents-- my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were only men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so I just pitched in as best as I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In retrospect, it might have been a foolish thing to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But as it was, it worked out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And time went by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And one nice day, my name was called during the major assembly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was taken to the main office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was handed a small brown envelope and my clothing in a bundle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in this envelope was my bar mitzvah watch, some other little personal things-- some kind of a thin, gold ring that I had gotten from a relative, the things that were taken from me when I was taken in there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it should give an insight into the German mentality of correctness and orderliness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Even under those circumstances, everything had to be according to the book.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
